        "ID": 378506,
        "Title": "2005年奥斯卡最佳动画入围：《怪物史瑞克2》",
        "Content": "<p><strong>精彩台词<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;color:#660000;\">：“我愿意做一个幸福快乐的公主，和我喜欢的怪物一齐生活在沼泽里面。”</span></strong></p><p><strong>影片点评：</strong>与第一集对经典童话额改写相比，《怪物史莱克2》对经典童话人物的吐槽和对暑期档大片的戏谑的戏仿，已经“贱”到了“无以复加”的地步。这让人很困惑，因为倘若对电影不熟悉，那么观赏这部电影的乐趣就要减半。幽默、卖萌、又毫不手软的穿靴子的猫是这部电影的最大亮点，也是最抢戏的配角。这个角色相当受欢迎，所以在不久之后，梦工厂拍拍摄了一部以它为主角的电影——当然，那部电影也恶搞了很多经典童话。</p><p><strong>惜败点评：</strong>影片还是搞笑有余而深度和情感不足。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul class=\"lh20\"><li><strong class=\"bold\">导演：</strong> <a class=\"mr6\" href=\"http://people.mtime.com/902542/\" rel=\"v:directedBy\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">安德鲁·亚当森</span></a> <a class=\"mr6\" href=\"http://people.mtime.com/899673/\" rel=\"v:directedBy\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">凯利·阿斯博瑞</span></a> <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/10681/fullcredits.html\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">更多<span class=\"gt\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;\">&gt;&gt;</span></span></span></a> </li><li><strong class=\"bold\">主演：</strong> <a class=\"mr6\" href=\"http://people.mtime.com/899773/\" rel=\"v:starring\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">麦克·梅尔斯</span></a> <a class=\"mr6\" href=\"http://people.mtime.com/915028/\" rel=\"v:starring\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">卡梅隆·迪亚茨</span></a> <a class=\"mr6\" href=\"http://people.mtime.com/899014/\" rel=\"v:starring\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">艾迪·墨菲</span></a> <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/10681/fullcredits.html\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">更多<span class=\"gt\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;\">&gt;&gt;</span></span></span></a> </li><li><strong class=\"bold\">类型：</strong> <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/movie/search/section/?type=Animation\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:genre\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">动画</span></a> / <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/movie/search/section/?type=Fantasy\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:genre\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">奇幻</span></a> / <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/movie/search/section/?type=Family\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:genre\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">家庭</span></a> / <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/movie/search/section/?type=Adventure\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:genre\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">冒险</span></a> / <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/movie/search/section/?type=Comedy\" target=\"_blank\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:genre\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">喜剧</span></a> </li><li><strong class=\"bold\">上映日期：</strong> <span content=\"2004-8-10\" _counted=\"undefined\" property=\"v:initialReleaseDate\">2004年8月10日 </span>&nbsp; 中国 &nbsp;<a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/10681/releaseinfo.html\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">更多<span class=\"gt\" _counted=\"undefined\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;\">&gt;&gt;</span></span></span></a> <p _counted=\"undefined\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"mt10 c_666\">延续了第一部的风格，继续对经典童话进行善意的颠覆。史莱克与菲奥纳公主回到公主的老家，但公主的父母很难接受这位女婿…… <a href=\"http://movie.mtime.com/10681/plots.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#2f688c;\">详细内容</span></a> </p>",
